%section.mod-intro
  .layout-wrap
    .heading
      %h1
        Innovative Mobile Apps & Games
        %span that help people learn a second language.

      %ul.os
        %li.android Android
        %li.ios iOS

  .map
    = image_tag 'apps.png', :alt => 'Screenshots of Native Tongue apps', :class => 'screenshots'

    .marker_container
      .marker.bubble1{:style => 'top: 240px; left: 230px'}
        = image_tag 'avatar.png'
        %p
          Love this app! Great for getting to know vocab, probably my favourite game on android right now, great development A+++
          %b (Spanish Smash review, Google Play)

      .marker.bubble2{:style => 'top: 280px; left: 460px'}
        = image_tag 'avatar.png'
        %p
          Great for getting to know vocab, probably my favourite game on android right now, great development A+++
          %b (Spanish Smash review, Google Play)

      .marker.bubble3{:style => 'top: 240px; left: 750px'}
        = image_tag 'avatar.png'
        %p
          It's like eating broccoli that tastes like cookies. I love your app "mandarin madness". The engagement is amazing, the aesthetics (music/illustration) are incredible.
          %b (Bruce Flaherty, Minnesota)

  .layout-wrap
    %ul.apps
      %li
        Mandarin Madness
        %ul
          %li= link_to 'iPhone & iPad', 'https://itunes.apple.com/app/learn-chinese-mandarin-madness/id494800742?mt=8', :class => 'button ios'
          %li= link_to 'Android', '#', :class => 'button android'
          %li= link_to 'Kindle Fire', '#', :class => 'button kindle'
      %li
        Spanish Smash
        %ul
          %li= link_to 'iPhone & iPad', 'https://itunes.apple.com/app/learn-spanish-spanish-smash/id524637598?mt=8', :class => 'button ios'
          %li= link_to 'Android', '#', :class => 'button android'
          %li= link_to 'Kindle Fire', '#', :class => 'button kindle'
      %li
        English Eruption
        %ul
          %li= link_to 'iPhone & iPad', 'https://itunes.apple.com/app/learn-english-english-eruption/id505864135?mt=8', :class => 'button ios'
          %li= link_to 'Android', '#coming-soon', :class => 'button android coming-soon'
          %li= link_to 'Kindle Fire', '#coming-soon', :class => 'button kindle coming-soon'

    %section.mod-usp
      %h1 Forget Boring flash cards. Play a game instead!
      %ul.left
        %li Learn more quickly than with flash cards.
        %li Learn to recognize both the text as well as the sound, spoken by a native speaker.
        %li 3 stages and 41 levels that each get progressively more difficult to ensure your mastery of a set of words.
